## Remarks  

> [!NOTE]
>  [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/includes/deprecatedcontent-md.md)]  

 <span data-ttu-id="3a114-103">Esse atributo deve ser usado apenas como opção de propriedade de dependência.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3a114-103">This attribute should only be used as dependency property option.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3a114-104">Atributos são ignorados se declarado em uma propriedade do .NET.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3a114-104">Attributes are ignored if declared on a .NET property.</span></span>  

 <span data-ttu-id="3a114-105">O <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.ValidationOptionAttribute> se destina a ser usado somente nas propriedades de metadados.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3a114-105">The <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.ValidationOptionAttribute> is intended to be used on Meta-properties only.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3a114-106">Ele será ignorado para propriedades de instância.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3a114-106">It will be ignored for instance properties.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3a114-107">Para obter mais informações, consulte [usando propriedades de atividade](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/974353d4-28f9-4202-890d-b36981876148) para obter mais detalhes.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3a114-107">For more information, see [Using Activity Properties](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/974353d4-28f9-4202-890d-b36981876148) for more details.</span></span>  

 <span data-ttu-id="3a114-108">Se o <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.ValidationOptionAttribute> não for especificado, o comportamento padrão é <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.ValidationOption.Optional?displayProperty=nameWithType>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3a114-108">If the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.ValidationOptionAttribute> is not specified, the behavior defaults to <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.ValidationOption.Optional?displayProperty=nameWithType>.</span></span>  

```csharp  
public sealed partial class Activity1: Activity  
{  
    public Activity1()  
    {  
    }  

    public static DependencyProperty MyPropertyProperty =   
        DependencyProperty.Register(  
            "MyProperty",   
            typeof(string),   
            typeof(Activity1),  
            new PropertyMetadata(  
                DependencyPropertyOptions.Metadata,  
                new ValidationOptionAttribute(ValidationOption.Required)));  

    [Browsable(true)]  
    [DesignerSerializationVisibility(DesignerSerializationVisibility.Visible)]  
    public string MyProperty  
    {  
        get  
        {  
            return ((string)(base.GetValue(Activity1.MyPropertyProperty)));  
        }  
        set  
        {  
            base.SetValue(Activity1.MyPropertyProperty, value);  
        }  
    }  
}  
```
